<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>الْمُتَّصِلُ وَالْمَوْصُولُ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٩٩.<span style="color:#006d98"> وَإِنْ تَصِلْ بِسَنَدٍ مَنْقُولَا … فَسَمِّهِ:</span> <span style="color:#6c6c00">«مُتَّصِلاً»</span>، <span style="color:#6c6c00">«مَوْصُولَا»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>١٠٠. سَوَاءٌ الْمَوْقُوفُ وَالْمَرْفُوعُ … وَلَمْ يَرَوْا أَنْ يَدْخُلَ الْمَقْطُوعُ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>